{"tid":88930,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"星期四考掃桿埔，有咩要注意？","createTime":"2017-01-21T03:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T03:14:14.000Z","uid":27403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13b11f45462db02ae302f53af85b100aa4bd8a31","tid":88930,"uid":27403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"考中午，多唔多死車，多唔多盲毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057574042ebbfc1513decb834d410fbc37eee441","tid":88930,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"好多，準備retake 吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688123ffb48994a57e321323a56bdc971eb539cd","tid":88930,"uid":27403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多，準備retake 吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9509a37e7dc1f705f825d2b4722a3560e6cd80e9","tid":88930,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"你估日日路面情況都一樣咩!你臨近新年先考，祝你好運，肯定多車！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8dd7df2ea8f7fd758c6f09b78bc6645fda2d15c","tid":88930,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:59:26.000Z","msg":"準備一杯水 一滴都唔好出黎呀<br />\n如果唔係 今次我打死你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753908e0cf3b00acf66fd5a85f432f814385c080","tid":88930,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>準備一杯水 一滴都唔好滴出黎呀<br />\n如果唔係 今次我打死你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cd2f7ca2c573956157b9c5198805912aacd99067","tid":88930,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:01:12.000Z","msg":"考果條 肥撚左"},{"pid":"bf3d9e8d9eac5d6d7883f0544294f5de10bb2866","tid":88930,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"南華會門口幾時都係咁多死車<br />\n第一次就係死喺嗰度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5452719848d524cfc57aa8b9160cce1e2b35eccb","tid":88930,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:05:37.000Z","msg":"最緊要兩個字 安全<br />\n你SHOW到比考官你渣得安全<br />\n有留意路面情況 應該都無死<br />\n其他野就聽天由命"},{"pid":"583a42bc19397e0a4645d2614271777d9edfa92b","tid":88930,"uid":42611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:27:52.000Z","msg":"留意斜坡起步, 唔好死火.<br />\n之後三手軚調頭泊位, 留意返停車位,再倒後.<br />\n泊位後出去路試, 小心落斜吊離合死火, 加路連山道轉東院道都幾多車.<br />\n之後考邊條線, 就祝你好運喇."},{"pid":"2600278fa1c97301d98a33bacb2c32301d471761","tid":88930,"uid":27403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"年廿九考，希望順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a65712d77c6e1869442e8a2a6cbbe3030bf745","tid":88930,"uid":74940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:57:10.000Z","msg":"掃桿埔中午條路多車到仆街（行車，死車都多）<br />\n祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26e7bb01decc7f25ffad061e7b6204007b24249","tid":88930,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"因為學校應該放緊假<br />\n所以應該係最容易考既時候黎"},{"pid":"644947bb85e9e046b1d77ad28d5dc201094d4c10","tid":88930,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"愈早開車愈好"},{"pid":"a76a24bd4642dc86b910bb06032370afb6cd9426","tid":88930,"uid":27537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:02:41.000Z","msg":"早d去，愈早愈愈好，多數考斜佬，記得望鏡，開車前望多兩望先行"},{"pid":"1d16a7597d12ec5e02b48530656ae19cf3d07a03","tid":88930,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:14:14.000Z","msg":"510<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}